<h2>Processing time</h2>
<p>Orders typically process within <strong>1–2 business days</strong>. During peak periods, processing may take a bit longer.</p>

<h2>Shipping methods & delivery</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Standard</strong>: 3–7 business days (after processing)</li>
  <li><strong>Expedited</strong>: 2–3 business days (after processing)</li>
</ul>
<p>Delivery estimates are not guaranteed and may vary by carrier, weather, and address verification.</p>

<h2>Tracking</h2>
<p>Once your order ships, we’ll provide a tracking number. Tracking can take up to 24 hours to update after the label is created.</p>

<h2>Questions</h2>
<p>Need help? Start with <a href="/search/">search</a> to find items, or browse <a href="/collections/sale/">sale</a> to see what’s available now.</p>
